\]

\end_inset

To prove the two sides were 
\emph on
not 
\emph default
equal
\emph on
 
\emph default
I only needed to go to order 2 in the series.
 To determine when the series 
\emph on
are 
\emph default
equal is more difficult; surprisingly, it all comes down to whether the
